---
title: Chicken Piccata with garlic butter sauce and roasted broccoli
description: This moreish chicken piccata is an Italian-inspired dish that originated in the US in the early 20th century. The term piccata refers to a method of cooking that involves dousing in flour and smothering in a buttery sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R11_W13_IE_IEXCLC0002-2_Main_high-fbafa805.jpg
